Author: A. Unique TensorFlower <gardener@tensorflow.org>
Date:   Thu Jul 7 15:07:26 2016 -0800

    Points links to the wide_n_deep.py example to master, and fixes a heading problem in the tf.contrib.learn quickstart.
    Change: 126857823

index 910e91e..d238b72 100644

-https://www.tensorflow.org/code/tensorflow/examples/learn/wide_n_deep_tutorial.py).
+https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/examples/learn/wide_n_deep_tutorial.py).

 3.  Install the pandas data analysis library. tf.learn doesn't require pandas, but it does support it, and this tutorial u
